<H3> <TI>   Tatarstan Decree on Stabilizing Economy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tatarstan Decree on Stabilizing Economy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0821A Kazan IZVESTIYA TATARSTANA in Russian 11 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944F0821A </F>
<F P=104>  Kazan IZVESTIYA TATARSTANA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
CSO 

<F P=106> ["Decree of the Supreme Soviet of the Republic of Tatarstan: </F>
On Priority Measures To Stabilize the Economy of the Republic of 
Tatarstan"] 
  [Text] The Supreme Soviet of the Republic of Tatarstan 
resolves: 
  1. To assume as a basis the "Priority Measures To Stabilize 
the Economy of the Republic of Tatarstan" drawn up and presented 
by the Government of the Republic of Tatarstan. 
  2. To instruct the Cabinet of Ministers of the Republic of 
Tatarstan to study the proposals and observations submitted by 
the people's deputies and also the findings of the standing 
commissions of the Supreme Soviet of the Republic of Tatarstan, 
to adopt the necessary measures, and to report at the next 
session of the Supreme Soviet of the Republic of Tatarstan. 
  3. That the Government of the Republic of Tatarstan shall, 
in 
accordance with the Constitution of the Republic of Tatarstan, 
the treaty of the Russian Federation and the Republic of 
Tatarstan "Delineation of Terms of Reference and the Mutual 
Delegation of Authority Between Organs of State Power of the 
Russian Federation and Organs of State Power of the Republic of 
Tatarstan," and the "Priority Measures To Stabilize the Economy 
of the Republic of Tatarstan," that have been assumed as a 
basis, draw up a State Program of Economic and Social Progress 
of the Republic of Tatarstan and present it to the Supreme 
Soviet of the Republic of Tatarstan in October 1994. 
  4. To exclude in connection with the adoption of this decree 
clause 2 of the decree of the Supreme Soviet of the Republic of 
Tatarstan of 21 April 1994 "Procedure of the Implementation of 
the Law of the Republic of Tatarstan 'Budget System of the 
Republic of Tatarstan for 1994.'" 
  To consider clauses 3, 4, and 5 of the said decree clauses 
2, 
3, and 4 respectively. 
  [Signed] F. Mukhametshin, chairman of the Supreme Soviet of 
the Republic of Tatarstan 
  Kazan, 8 June 1994 

</TEXT>

