<H3> <TI>   Tatarstan Decree on Social Protection </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tatarstan Decree on Social Protection </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0821B Kazan IZVESTIYA TATARSTANA in Russian 11 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
