<H3> <TI>   Distribution of Tatarstan Wage Fund Noted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Distribution of Tatarstan Wage Fund Noted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0793B Kazan IZVESTIYA TATARSTANA in Russian 8 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
