<H3> <TI>   Tatarstan Delegation Visits Komi </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tatarstan Delegation Visits Komi </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0806B Kazan RESPUBLIKA TATARSTAN in Russian 9 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
