<H3> <TI>   Russia's Choice Caucus Delegates Selected </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russia's Choice Caucus Delegates Selected </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0912A St. Petersburg SMENA in Russian 7 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944E0912A </F>
