<H3> <TI>   8,000 Joint Ventures in St Petersburg </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    8,000 Joint Ventures in St Petersburg </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0924A St. Petersburg SANKT PETERBURGSKIYE VEDOMOSTI in 
Russian 9 Jun 94 p 5 </F>

<F P=103> 944E0924A </F>
<F P=104>  St. Petersburg SANKT PETERBURGSKIYE VEDOMOSTI </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


