<H3> <TI>   Commission To Regulate Securities Market </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Commission To Regulate Securities Market </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0924C Moscow MOSKOVSKIYE NOVOSTI in Russian No 21, 22-29 
May 94 p C7 </F>

