<H3> <TI>   Resistance to Following U.S. Lead on Korean Nuclear Issue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Resistance to Following U.S. Lead on Korean Nuclear Issue </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Sympathy Toward DPRK Urged </H4>

<F P=102> 94WP0096A Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA in Russian 31 May 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 94WP0096A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA </F>
