<H3> <TI>   MFER Instruction Regulating Export Licenses </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    MFER Instruction Regulating Export Licenses </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0394B Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 21 May 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0394B </F>
