<H3> <TI>   Russian Accounting System To Conform to World Standards </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Accounting System To Conform to World Standards </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0394C Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 17 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0394C </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
