<H3> <TI>   EBRD, Deutsche Bank To Finance Rostov Business Center </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    EBRD, Deutsche Bank To Finance Rostov Business Center </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0405B Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 27 May 94 p 9 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0405B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
