<H3> <TI>   Ministry Responds to Pension Fund Concerns </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ministry Responds to Pension Fund Concerns </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1478A Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA in Russian 11 Jun 94 
p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1478A </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


