<H3> <TI>   Regional Polls on Interethnic Issues </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Regional Polls on Interethnic Issues </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1410A Almaty VESTNIK KAZAKHSTANA in Russian 7 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1410A </F>
