<H3> <TI>   Rail Link to Iran Planned </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rail Link to Iran Planned </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1468D Baku GUNAY in Russian 15 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1468D </F>
<F P=104>  Baku GUNAY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
