<H3> <TI>   Russians, Estonians Polled on Political, Social Issues </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russians, Estonians Polled on Political, Social Issues </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P50158A Helsinki HUFVUSDSTADSBLADET in Swedish 8 Jun 94 p 
