<DATE1>   31 May 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> BALTIC STATES </F>
<F P=101> LATVIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Election Results From Latvia's Largest Cities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Election Results From Latvia's Largest Cities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1476A Riga LABRIT in Latvian 31 May 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1476A </F>
