<F P=106> [Article based on Russian Goskomstat Materials: "Will They </F>
Help To Take Us Away From the Brink of the Abyss?] 
  [Text] The economic crisis is not dying away. The 
materials of Russian Goskomstat are convincing indication of 
this. At the end of May, the President of Russia passed a group 
of edicts for a true breakthrough in the critical situation. 
<H5>  Macroeconomic Indicators </H5>
  The basic indicators characterizing the January-April 1994 
results are presented below: 


