  The mass of monetary income of the fifth group of the 
population exceeded the mass of monetary income of the first 
group in April 1992 by a factor of 2.9, 1993 -- by a factor of 
6.2 and 1994 -- a factor of 5. 
  The change in amount of the subsistence minimum for the 
population of the Russian Federation in 1994 (determined in 
accordance with the methodology of the Russian Ministry of 
Labor) is shown in the following table (on the average -- thous. 
rubles per month): 


---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |              |including                                   | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |Entire popula-|Fit for work  |Pensioners    |Children      | 
|              |tion          |              |              |              | 
