<H3> <TI>   DELOVOY MIR Economic Statistics, 25 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    DELOVOY MIR Economic Statistics, 25 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0902A Moscow DELOVOY MIR in Russian 25 May 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 944E0902A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow DELOVOY MIR </F>
