<H5>  Past-Due Back Pay Liabilities </H5>
  The number of enterprises having liabilities with respect to 
back pay and other labor remuneration-related pay-outs dropped 
somewhat in the beginning of May as compared to the beginning of 
April; the ratio of past-due liabilities in relation to 
enterprises' payroll also dropped. In absolute terms, past-due 
back pay liabilities increased insignificantly over April. 
  The data on the number of enterprises having past-due back 
